    dc:description "Figure 34. Holotype male of Chelonus diversus Walker, 1874 (= Phanerotoma (Phanerotoma) diversa (Walker, 1874)): (a) labels (b) lateral habitus (c) head, frontal view (d) head, dorsal view (e) head, lateral view (f) mesoscutum and scutellum, dorsal view (g) propodeum, dorsal view (h) metasoma, dorsal view (i) mesosoma, lateral view (j) wings." ;
